From the problem data:

| Account | Amount | Date |
|---------------|--------------|--------------|
| Main Business Revenue | 16388736.33 | 2024-02-05 |
| Total Revenue | 16388736.33 | 2024-02-05 |
| ... | ... | ... |

The income from core operating activities is "Main Business Revenue" which has the value 16388736.33.

Therefore, the solution is:

```json
{"solution": {"value": "16388736.33"} }
```
